Uj4PlBFUA1y6rjDbj-CpDCtfw651nAYoijSDobJhaG573PEGHjdZYE&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_ss=8&oh=00_AfzxIgKZ6ksMyz1gLTFXZmXaivs1hKmMrv3WC84UluxkHA&oe=69BE54D1"},"tabletIcon":{"uri":"https:\/\/scontent.oculuscdn.com\/v\/t64.5771-25\/39031561_126248162630313_6579503751297065747_n.webp?stp=c0.0.720.720a_dst-webp_s64x64&_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Sr7SEKXtZ6gQ7kNvwHc35fb&_nc_oc=AdlTeV5m5bbowUj4PlBFUA1y6rjDbj-CpDCtfw651nAYoijSDobJhaG573PEGHjdZYE&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_ss=8&oh=00_AfwevHmOfUz1xJ9UmxpQ_rDnVIpRNrrZcoDNmtqLVTiSUg&oe=69BE54D1"}},"is_early_access_review":false,"score":5,"review_description":"If you thought Beatsaber was a workout, just give this game five minutes of your time and you'll come to realize how many towels you'll need. Looking at this game critically, I say that it is a perfect concept for a vr racing game, rather than being stuck in a vehicle, you are the vehicle. The mix of Mariokart esque power ups and the movement of Jet Set Radio Future blend incredbly well and lend themselves to a unique experience! That being said however, for any new player it will take a few days to grasp the running mechanic, but once you do you'll be in for the time of your life. My final note is, unfortunantely due the current state of VR, online mulitiplayer is lacking, however this isn't to fault Survios, because they put out an amazing game with immense replayability and a sizeable amount of content for the price. Sprint Vector is a solid game with loads of content and should be a mainstay for any VR user.","review_title":"Run, Jump, and sweat like heck!","date":1609043993,"translated_review_title":null,"translated_review_description":null,"translated_developer_response_body":null,"developer_response":null,"review_helpful_count":25,"review_rank_by_viewer":null,"reported_by_viewer":false,"__typename":"QualityRating"},"cursor":"AQHStG6vsYVNI98tYi3mupl_nZCQdqkCOAqdaDgdgTM2H-psVICMMa7RTcQuaNNhPDIm"},{"node":{"id":"12711502530432